 (b) such consequential provision; and
 (c) such savings,as he considers necessary or expedient in preparation for or in connection with the coming into force of any provision of this Act or the operation of any enactment which is repealed or amended by a provision of this Act during any period when the repeal or amendment is not wholly in force.

    (7) Regulations under this section may modify any enactment contained in this or in any other Act and any instrument made under an Act of Parliament.

